data.description: Welcome to your solar-powered dream home. 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom 2-Car garage, WATERFRONT home nestled in the welcoming community of Park Lake Estates. Come enjoy the peace and tranquility of waterfront living with No flood insurance required & optional $30/Annual Association membership! Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-lit interior that effortlessly blends comfort and style. The home features a formal living room that seamlessly connects to the open kitchen and dining area. The kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting ample cabinet and countertop space, complete with an expansive breakfast bar. This area flows gracefully into the welcoming family room, creating an ideal space for hosting and entertaining guests. Step outside to the back porch, which offers breathtaking views of the serene lake. From here, you can access the beautifully paved back patio, a perfect setting to unwind and relish in the delightful Florida weather year round. Whether you're gathering around the bonfire pit or firing up the grill, this space will quickly become your favorite outdoor retreat. This property not only offers comfort and convenience but also features modern sustainability with its recently installed solar panels making the average electric bill less then $80 monthly! Home is conveniently located just a stone's throw away from popular shopping spots like Downtown New Port Richey, Mitchell Plaza, Multiple Hospital's, School's, Restaurants and only 35-Minutes to Tampa International Airport. Don't miss out on the chance to call this exceptional property your own. Reach out to us to arrange a showing today!
